metadata.name: Guardians of the Valley - Azuki #8433 + #8833
metadata.description:
Commission piece done for Snow.eth 's Azukis - #8433 and #8833.

They are the guardian couple of the Zuki garden. 
They have slain a lot of demons in their prime. Their blades will seal the souls of the damned within it for eternity. Reminds me of Totsuka blade of Itachi.

You dare not cross paths with them, if you have evil intentions.
